snippet.title: Knights & Guns Nintendo Switch Trailer
snippet.description:
From the publisher of Nintendo Switch titles Urban Flow, Moto Rush GT, Paratopic and Fatum Betula comes a new arcade game!

Inspired by PANG, Metal Slug and the Bug Butcher, the new running and gunning Knights & Guns is out now on Nintendo Switch!
